article.description: — Luis Kortright had 15 points in Rhode Island's 76-72 victory against Yale on Sunday night.
article.headline: Kortright helps Rhode Island earn 76-72 victory over Yale
article.linkText: Kortright helps Rhode Island earn 76-72 victory over Yale
article.story: KINGSTON, R.I. -- — Luis Kortright had 15 points in Rhode Island's 76-72 victory against Yale on Sunday night. Kortright also contributed five rebounds for the Rams (5-2). Zek Montgomery scored 14 points and added nine rebounds. Tyson Brown finished 5 of 5 from the floor to finish with 10 points. Danny Wolf led the way for the Bulldogs (4-3) with 19 points, four assists and four blocks. Bez Mbeng added 18 points and three steals for Yale. John Poulakidas also recorded 16 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
